{"tid":1928729,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒利亞：如英超踢不完 讓利記封王不公平","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T18:24:51.000Z","uid":69568,"like":55,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a723b0758e628f7899692951608d50ccda340f0a","tid":1928729,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"舒利亞：如英超踢不完 讓利記封王不公平<br />\n更多<br />\n朗尼回想賽前帶C朗去麥記<br />\n<br />\n英超因新冠肺炎疫情而暫停至4月3日。韋斯咸副主席嘉倫柏迪主張如賽事真不能完成，就該取消今季及判成績無效。<br />\n<br />\n舒利亞亦說：「如果今季真的未能完成，當然這是大件事，根本不能定出贏家輸家。對某些球會來說是苛刻且可怕的，特別是利物浦。」<br />\n<br />\n這位前英格蘭國腳認為，雖然利物浦只需多6分就可鎖定錦標，但始終數字上未做到，取消今季是無可奈何的選擇。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=bdb3854c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"4f90f48236d8ea2a26321d9d1fe8ece9cae2e4ae","tid":1928729,"uid":199081,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"輸痢亞死獌狗!"},{"pid":"f125bf1dea7f4a7f52bcc16eab8cafb5b87a59d1","tid":1928729,"uid":38189,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"舒利亞得一個英超 唔想利物浦都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7da3a2c3212d84bba3fa53be4d03a830bc25ac","tid":1928729,"uid":5191,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"內文邊到寫唔公平<br />\n利申 文盲"},{"pid":"de1e6e7ecf0fe02965aa545998f474483ffad9e8","tid":1928729,"uid":69568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"Alan Shearer says Liverpool can't be given Premier League title if season isn't completed<br />\n<br />\nBy&nbsp;Rob Hoskin<br />\n<br />\nLiverpool face an anxious wait as the Premier League decide what to do with the rest of the season.<br />\nThe Reds are just two wins from winning their first ever Premier League title after an incredible campaign that has seen them race into a 25-point lead.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, there is now a genuine chance the rest of the campaign can&rsquo;t be completed due to the coronavirus pandemic. It&rsquo;s already been postponed for three weeks so hopes of it returning in April seem unrealistic.<br />\nSo what happens if the season is declared null and void?<br />\nShould Liverpool still be awarded the Premier League title because they&rsquo;re so far clear?<br />\n<br />\nWell,&nbsp;Premier League&nbsp;legend Alan Shearer thinks not.<br />\n&ldquo;Not completing the&nbsp;season has to be the very last option on the table,&rdquo;&nbsp;Shearer wrote.<br />\n<br />\nIf, and it is a huge if, the season cannot be completed then there is no way you can have a winner or loser.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;As harsh and as horrible as that would be for some clubs, none more so than&nbsp;Liverpool,&nbsp; it is the only outcome.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;If you cannot complete the fixtures then you cannot go handing out titles or consider relegating anybody.<br />\n&quot;But I cannot see how it would be fair to hand them the title &mdash; despite the fact it&nbsp; is obvious nobody is going to catch them.<br />\n&quot;They only need six points to wrap it up but they haven&rsquo;t got them yet so for that reason it has to be declared null and void.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It would be very different if the season was suspended after they had got the points to win it.&nbsp;But they haven&rsquo;t and however horrible a scenario it would be, it&rsquo;s the only option.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s certainly a tricky situation to deal with as nothing like this has ever happened before.<br />\n<br />\nFor Liverpool to smash multiple records and be on the brink of glory and then have that snatched away from them is cruel.<br />\nBut there&rsquo;s also a decision to be made in terms of relegation. Do the bottom three clubs get demoted? Or do they get a stay of execution?<br />\n<br />\nThe Premier League is set to have a meeting on Thursday where they will attempt to iron out all these logistical nightmares."},{"pid":"1328bf3b1baada4faae92589f597b00294fa849d","tid":1928729,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f90f48236d8ea2a26321d9d1fe8ece9cae2e4ae","tid":1928729,"uid":199081,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"輸痢亞死獌狗!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"8a09cc3e7c7e8c985a386a043469ef0f62ba6c0b","tid":1928729,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死曼狗"},{"pid":"c195640dfba9576a95d56e473ea649df79d8578d","tid":1928729,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f125bf1dea7f4a7f52bcc16eab8cafb5b87a59d1","tid":1928729,"uid":38189,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"舒利亞得一個英超 唔想利物浦都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"我哋利物浦好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c49c6dc121126b11c7d16e7cd12384007828d","tid":1928729,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b70eabbb494e1b8dbbe6d5ae77568c2a583d1c","tid":1928729,"uid":339053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"點解話舒利亞係49000?"},{"pid":"5ab18762b07b31b089946f419c1075cced972f00","tid":1928729,"uid":304141,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78d58767057079d06714ec6249a3082f5f3f5323","tid":1928729,"uid":172226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"想睇更多：<br />\n朗尼回想賽前帶C朗去麥記<br />\nC朗個時應該未戒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢細個窮到要係m記乞包食 勁慘<br />